<block>
    <view s-if="{{}}"></view>
    <view s-if="{{public}}"></view>
    <view s-if="ab && cd"></view>
    <view s-elif="{{abc}}"></view>
    <view s-elif="ab && cd"></view>
    <view s-else></view>

    <view s-for="list"></view>
    <view s-for="item, index in list"></view>
    <view s-for="item,index in list trackBy item.id"></view>
    <view s-for-index="abc"></view>
    <view s-for-item="abc"></view>

    <view bindtap="package"></view>
    <view bindtap="tap"></view>
    <view bind:tap="tap"></view>
    <view bind:tap="{{tap}}"></view>
    <view bind:tap="{{'tap'}}"></view>
    <view catchtap="tap"></view>
    <view catch:tap="{{tap}}"></view>
    <view capture-bind:tap="tap"></view>
    <view capture-catch:tap="{{tap}}"></view>
    <view mut-bind:tap="tap"></view>
    <view bind:touchmove.stop="stop"></view>
    <view bind:touch-move.stop="{{stop}}"></view>
    
</block>
